<br>
That was enough for me, at the time.<br>
<br>
Now that I'm tweaking every point of regen, every last HP, etc, and with some people running around talking about Symbol + PotG having more hp than Aego, etc...<br>
<br>
Who's done the math?<br>
<br>
Near as I can tell, group aego beats the PotG + Symbol thing, though I could be wrong....And stacking...maybe there's more to it than that.  Anyways, I know Raz had done some numbers on regen, coming up with 5 hp = 1.67 mana...and I don't know off hand the number of raw hp (non regen) and what it equals in mana.<br>
<br>
